title: Can anybody help me identify these 2 fonts?
content:
Hi guys!

Can anyone help me identify these fonts? I've already searched on WhatTheFont and Identifont, but did not find any convincing result...

comments.content: Chemin de Vie is Seattle Regular. packaged with clickart disc from Broderbund.

Many thanks defiantone!  
For the first one the match is OK, though the letter V seems to be different. Maybe it was reworked on the logo...
